name: Petzl Ange Finesse Quickdraw
description: A quickdraw equipped with one Ange L and one Angle S biner to keep your rock, alpine or ice rack nice and light, without sacrificing function or strength.H-shaped profile offers good strength to weight ratio.MonoFil keylock wire gates offer smooth opening and closing.10mm Finesse Dyneema sling.String keeper holds the rope-end biner in place.
